@startuml
title Viaverse Privacy / KVKK Data Subject Request — Sequence Diagram

actor User
participant "Client" as Client
participant "API Gateway / BFF" as BFF
participant "privacy-service" as Privacy
participant "identity-service" as Identity
participant "Domain Services" as Domains
participant "audit-service" as Audit
queue "Outbox / Kafka" as Kafka

User -> Client : request export/delete/correction
Client -> BFF : POST /privacy/requests
BFF -> Privacy : createDSAR(command)
Privacy -> Identity : verify account ownership
Identity --> Privacy : verified
Privacy -> Domains : collect/export or delete/anonymize commands
Domains --> Privacy : completion receipts
Privacy -> Audit : write DSAR audit log
Privacy -> Kafka : DataExportReady / DataDeleted / ConsentChanged
Privacy --> BFF : request status/result
BFF --> Client : show result / download link

note bottom
privacy-service coordinates user rights.
Domain services execute their own export/delete/anonymize logic and return receipts.
end note
@enduml
